      <title>代码块功能验收样例</title>
      <link href="/hexo/posts/1c24dade.html"/>
      <url>/hexo/posts/1c24dade.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文档用于全面检验博客主题的代码块功能，特别是在 PJAX 动态加载后，各项功能是否依然完好。</p><p>主要检验点：</p><ol><li>多种语言的 <strong>语法高亮</strong> 是否正确。</li><li>鼠标悬浮时 <strong>“复制”按钮</strong> 是否出现。</li><li>点击“复制”按钮后，内容是否能被 <strong>完整、正确地</strong> 粘贴到记事本中。</li><li>带有 <strong>标题</strong> 或 <strong>行号高亮</strong> 的高级功能是否正常。</li></ol><hr><h2 id="1-基础代码块"><a href="#1-基础代码块" class="headerlink" title="1. 基础代码块"></a>1. 基础代码块</h2><p>这是一个没有指定语言的普通代码块，通常会以纯文本样式显示。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Hello, World!</span><br><span class="line">This is a plain text code block.</span><br><span class="line">There should be no syntax highlighting here.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="2-带语法高亮的语言"><a href="#2-带语法高亮的语言" class="headerlink" title="2. 带语法高亮的语言"></a>2. 带语法高亮的语言</h2><h3 id="JavaScript"><a href="#JavaScript" class="headerlink" title="JavaScript"></a>JavaScript</h3><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// A modern JavaScript example with async/await</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">async</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">fetchData</span>(<span class="params">url</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">const</span> response = <span class="keyword">await</span> <span class="title function_">fetch</span>(url);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (!response.<span class="property">ok</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">throw</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Error</span>(<span class="string">`HTTP error! status: <span class="subst">$&#123;response.status&#125;</span>`</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">const</span> data = <span class="keyword">await</span> response.<span class="title function_">json</span>();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Data fetched successfully:&quot;</span>, data);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> data;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">catch</span> (error) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">error</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Failed to fetch data:&quot;</span>, error);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Python"><a href="#Python" class="headerlink" title="Python"></a>Python</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># A simple Python class</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Greeter</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="params">self, name</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.name = name</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">greet</span>(<span class="params">self, loud=<span class="literal">False</span></span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> loud:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&quot;HELLO, <span class="subst">&#123;self.name.upper()&#125;</span>!&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&quot;Hello, <span class="subst">&#123;self.name&#125;</span>&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Let&#x27;s test it</span></span><br><span class="line">greeter = Greeter(<span class="string">&quot;Bettermyx&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">greeter.greet()</span><br><span class="line">greeter.greet(loud=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Go"><a href="#Go" class="headerlink" title="Go"></a>Go</h3><figure class="highlight go"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">package</span> main</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="string">&quot;fmt&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// A simple struct in Go</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> Vector <span class="keyword">struct</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">X, Y <span class="type">int</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">func</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">v := Vector&#123;<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">fmt.Printf(<span class="string">&quot;Vector v has coordinates: X=%d, Y=%d\n&quot;</span>, v.X, v.Y)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="YAML-常用于-Hugo-配置"><a href="#YAML-常用于-Hugo-配置" class="headerlink" title="YAML (常用于 Hugo 配置)"></a>YAML (常用于 Hugo 配置)</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Example of Hugo config front matter</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">params:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">author:</span> <span class="string">Bettermyx</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">description:</span> <span class="string">&quot;每天进步一点点。&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">comments:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">enabled:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">giscus:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">&quot;better-myx/better-myx.github.io&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">repoID:</span> <span class="string">&quot;R_kgDOQThkjA&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Shell-Bash"><a href="#Shell-Bash" class="headerlink" title="Shell &#x2F; Bash"></a>Shell &#x2F; Bash</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#!/bin/bash</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># A simple shell script to list files</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;Listing files in the current directory:&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> file <span class="keyword">in</span> *; <span class="keyword">do</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> [ -f <span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$file</span>&quot;</span> ]; <span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot; - <span class="variable">$file</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">fi</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">done</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="3-高级功能测试"><a href="#3-高级功能测试" class="headerlink" title="3. 高级功能测试"></a>3. 高级功能测试</h2><h3 id="带标题的代码块"><a href="#带标题的代码块" class="headerlink" title="带标题的代码块"></a>带标题的代码块</h3><p>你的主题可能支持为代码块添加标题或文件名。</p><figure class="highlight go"><figcaption><span>&#123;title</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">package</span> main</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="string">&quot;fmt&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">func</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">fmt.Println(<span class="string">&quot;This code block should have a title: main.go&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="行号高亮"><a href="#行号高亮" class="headerlink" title="行号高亮"></a>行号高亮</h3><p>检查特定行是否能被高亮显示。</p><figure class="highlight python"><figcaption><span>&#123;title</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Highlighter</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    This is a docstring for the class.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    This line (3) should be highlighted.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    &quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">process_lines</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># These three lines (5-7) should be highlighted as a block.</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">3</span>):</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&quot;Processing line <span class="subst">&#123;i+<span class="number">1</span>&#125;</span>&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Done.&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="4-验证步骤"><a href="#4-验证步骤" class="headerlink" title="4. 验证步骤"></a>4. 验证步骤</h2><ol><li><strong>直接访问</strong>：直接在浏览器中打开本页面，检查所有代码块的语法高亮是否正常，复制功能是否可用。</li><li><strong>PJAX 切换</strong>：<ul><li>先访问博客的<strong>主页</strong>或者<strong>其他任何文章</strong>。</li><li>然后，通过点击站内链接<strong>导航到本页面</strong>。</li><li>再次检查所有代码块的高亮和复制功能。如果此时依然正常，说明你的 PJAX 集成非常成功！</li></ul></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
